plugins/forge-app-design/eval/quality/
plugins/forge-app-design/eval/**/*-report*.json
plugins/forge-app-design/eval/**/*-report*.md
plugins/forge-app-design/eval/**/quality-report.json
plugins/forge-app-design/eval/**/quality-report.md

# Figma 设计稿源文件（本地参考用，不入仓）
figma-code/

